column2: Hello, Hello? Do you read me?
Thank goodness! We have run out of fuel! Can you help us please?
Great. We are at <COORDS>. Just dock at our ship.
Great. We are at <COORDS>. Just dock at our ship. We can negotiate a price when you are on board.
All right, but for a price.
Yes I am. Consider yourself darwin award winners
May you rot in Hell! You poor heartless SOB. If I ever get my hands on you ....
We've run out of fuel. Please respond. Hello?
